text: Ohkay Owingeh is a census-designated place (CDP) in Rio Arriba County, New Mexico, United States and a federally recognized tribe of Native American Pueblo people. The 2020 census found that 1,464 people lived in Ohkay Owingeh, with 6,580 in the surrounding Census County Division. ==References== Category:Census-designated places in New Mexico
title: Ohkay Owingeh, New Mexico
